Review: I was like they are all gonna die what are they gonna ea- ohhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh.
Put Sterling K. Brown in more movies, I demand it.
Kinda need a solo Dr. Dre and Ice Cube movie that goes into more depth.
I can’t imagine shooting some of these scenes multiple times, the actors must’ve felt so uncomfortable while doing it.
Pacing is crazy bad in this wow.
If only this had a competent lead actor.
Glenn Howerton masterclass, did not see that coming. Also the goat Jay Baruchal finally doing another movie, feels like I haven’t seen him in anything since This is the End.
Still one of the greatest Oscar wins I’ve seen.

Fuck this movie. I should’ve known I was in trouble when the opening credits rolled. Great song but like no. It put me in the mood for a sports movie but instead this shit unfolds. Whoever chose that song needs to be banned from working on films indefinitely.
